          " Step 10: Assemble the Kimbap: Place a bamboo rolling mat on a clean surface. Place a sheet of dried seaweed on the mat, shiny side down. Spread the seasoned rice evenly on the seaweed, leaving a small border. Arrange the filling ingredients in a line across the center of the rice.",
